The Secretary to Rivers State Government (SSG) Dr Tammy Danagogo has said Governor Nyesom Wike deserves the presidential ticket of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP). Danagogo, who spoke in Port Harcourt on Monday, described Wike as a leader, whose tremendous accomplishments were visible for all to see. He said: “Governor Wike has an unwavering commitment to the development of Nigeria, and he will serve the nation with courage, commitment and the fear of God.   FG executes 800 roads, bridge projects – Lai Mohammed     HURIWA blasts Multichoice over hike in DStv, Gotv packages     Bandits didn’t shutdown Kaduna Airport, we killed 12 of them…   “Governor Wike has the Midas touch to rescue Nigeria from the problems bedevilling the nation. He genuinely loves Nigeria and will be a courageous, proactive, pragmatic and strategic leader. “As President, I know that he will faithfully implement programs and policies that will stem the ravaging insecurity and transform Nigeria. He has done it in Rivers State. He did it in the Federal Ministry of Education. He can do it at the Presidency.”